Package: scrapol
Title: Scraping Politicians' Party and District Information
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hui", "Zhou", , "huizhou68@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7381-5487"))
Description: Scraping American politicians' party and district information based on Ballotpedia. According to Ballotpedia's policy, crawlers are allowed only between 06:00 and 08:45 UTC (GMT) with a maximum rate of one page every 5 seconds.
